longBusinessSummary: Kingfisher Metals Corp. engages in the acquisition and development of mineral properties in British Columbia, Canada. The company primarily explores for gold, copper, silver, and zinc deposits. It holds 100% interests in the Ecstall property covering 28,407 hectares located in Northwest British Columbia; the Goldrange project covering 36,692 hectares located in Central British Columbia; and the Thibert project covering 12,475 hectares located to the north of Dease Lake. Kingfisher Metals Corp. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
